HEADWORD: Dactylopterous
<hw>Dac`tyl*op"ter*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>da`ktylos</grk> finger + <ets><grk>pte`ryx</grk></ets> wing,
fin.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having the inferior rays of the
